  "remarks": "\nOje Parvaz Mado Nafar Company “Mado Company” is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 in that it has provided or made available for use by the Russian military components and engines for Unmanned Aerial Vehicles (UAVs) that could contribute to destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
